Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.16,0:00:41.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それは…俺のものだぁー！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.79,0:00:44.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百っ鬼丸ぅー！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.63,0:00:51.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,返せ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.13,0:00:53.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,返す、だと…？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.13,0:00:55.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,笑止！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.59,0:00:59.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これは、お前のものではない！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.68,0:01:02.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,取り戻しに来たは我らのほうだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.60,0:01:05.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なに…？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.48,0:01:13.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こら！おとなしくしろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.78,0:01:17.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大丈夫だ、今みんなで逃げる相談すっから！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.16,0:01:24.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうどう！まったく…こんなに暴れるなんて。やっぱり…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.58,0:01:25.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,鬼神か？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.00,0:01:28.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いや…そいつはわかんねぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.71,0:01:33.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,けど、大事をとって女子供だけは少し国ざかいから離れたほうがいい。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.21,0:01:36.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戦があるのは間違いねぇからな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.18,0:01:38.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もう嫌だよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.72,0:01:40.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あっちやこっちへ行かされて…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.97,0:01:42.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どこ行ったって同じさ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.31,0:01:46.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おい！待て！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.69,0:01:50.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの様子…只事ではないぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.36,0:01:54.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,様子を確かめてくる。逃げるのはそのあとだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.23,0:01:55.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私も行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.07,0:02:00.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.24,0:02:04.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これは俺のだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.29,0:02:07.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,違う！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.92,0:02:16.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今やこれは醍醐の…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.47,0:02:19.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そして醍醐の手足
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.55,0:02:23.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もがれては国は立ち行かん。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.31,0:02:25.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いや、すでに揺らいでいる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.10,0:02:29.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,貴様が鬼神との約定を破ったせいで、
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.52,0:02:31.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もはや猶予はない。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.48,0:02:34.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,民のため、貴様のすべてを今！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.48,0:02:36.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,醍醐の血肉といたす！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.03,0:02:41.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,勝手を言うなぁー！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.16,0:00:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.79,0:00:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.63,0:00:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Give them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.13,0:00:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Give them back?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.13,0:00:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.59,0:00:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,These were never yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.68,0:01:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We are the ones here \Nto reclaim what is ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.60,0:01:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.48,0:01:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, easy now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.78,0:01:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, \Nwe'll find a place to run away to.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.16,0:01:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there. \NI've never seen him act so wildly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.58,0:01:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be the demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.00,0:01:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.71,0:01:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But we should get the women and children \Naway from the border just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.21,0:01:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There will be a war anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.18,0:01:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sick of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.72,0:01:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Being moved here and there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.97,0:01:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same wherever we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.31,0:01:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.69,0:01:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.36,0:01:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go check. We can run later.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.23,0:01:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.07,0:02:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.24,0:02:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.29,0:02:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No, they aren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.92,0:02:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,These are Daigo's eyes now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.47,0:02:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And Daigo's limbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.55,0:02:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The land will crumble \Nif they're taken away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.31,0:02:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already on the verge of collapsing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.10,0:02:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you broke the contract \Nwith the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.52,0:02:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.48,0:02:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We must take all of you \Nfor the sake of the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.48,0:02:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We will devour you for Daigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.03,0:02:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.38,0:02:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Betrayed this world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.59,0:03:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And it simmers within
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.80,0:03:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Rupturing my innards
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.02,0:03:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Swelling a reddish black
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.15,0:03:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the sun burnt skin ruptures
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.86,0:03:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a light  \N in the depths of the seething darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.70,0:03:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Confirming each other's voices  \N in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.87,0:03:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,As if to stroke with wet fingertips
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to touch you one day
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.89,0:03:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a light  \N in the depths of the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.06,0:03:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Confirming each other's voices  \N in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.23,0:04:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,As if to stroke with wet fingertips
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.44,0:04:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to touch you one day
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,#23 The story of the demons
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.97,0:04:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Tahomaru! Mutsu and Hyogo, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-Bro! \N-Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.02,0:04:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't last a second out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.94,0:04:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.15,0:04:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure Hyakkimaru \Nwould even be able to recognize you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.36,0:04:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The other three are \Nnot themselves either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.45,0:04:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I know this feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.91,0:04:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm positive of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.83,0:04:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt it at the Hall of Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.09,0:05:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hall of Hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.59,0:05:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.05,0:05:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's where the statues of \Nthe 12 demons that ate Hyakkimaru are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.35,0:05:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.89,0:05:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,one of the 12 failed to devour him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.94,0:05:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. It all makes sense now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.19,0:05:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why Hyakkimaru lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.15,0:05:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And is now being chased by demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.99,0:05:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They're trying to get back \Nwhat they failed to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.62,0:05:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why hasn't bro gotten \Nhis body parts back for a while now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.12,0:05:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What parts are still missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.33,0:05:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,His arms and his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.55,0:05:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Your answer may lie \Nwith those three out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.97,0:05:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The power of demons \Nresides within them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.60,0:05:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a terrible struggle \Nover body parts now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.19,0:06:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Between Hyakkimaru and the 12th demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.03,0:06:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All because of the contract made \Nby my husband, Daigo Kagemitsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This land cannot prosper \Nwithout Hyakkimaru's sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.29,0:06:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why Tahomaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.67,0:06:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.05,0:06:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody catch that horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.80,0:06:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hold on! \N-Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.31,0:06:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyogo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyogo...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.33,0:07:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mutsu! Hyogo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.66,0:07:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.69,0:08:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Was this horse your...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.44,0:08:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyogo! Mutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.78,0:08:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.20,0:08:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You will create... a land of peace...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you mustn't go, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.21,0:08:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mutsu, Hyogo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be joking, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.23,0:08:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We would follow you \Neven into the depths of hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.39,0:09:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-Bro... \N-Hyakkimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.20,0:09:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.17,0:09:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.72,0:10:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.51,0:10:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.35,0:10:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, please stand back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.69,0:10:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Tahomaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.02,0:10:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you still pity that thing, even now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.19,0:10:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a curse upon our land.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.37,0:10:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.66,0:10:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.98,0:10:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A beast it may be, but the bond \Nof mother and child is likewise strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.65,0:11:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,These are my hands. Mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.29,0:11:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does everyone get in my way?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.67,0:11:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...the body you regain  \N will be stained with human blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.34,0:11:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you still be human then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.26,0:11:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Human? What is human?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.68,0:11:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.72,0:11:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A curse upon our land.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.85,0:11:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's mine! I'm getting it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.10,0:11:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so wrong about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.58,0:11:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.26,0:12:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gotten his arms back,  \N so his reach is longer than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.46,0:12:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.96,0:12:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The body you regain will be stained...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.88,0:12:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But still, I will...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.16,0:13:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I stop bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.41,0:13:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it may be impossible to stop them \Nuntil one or the other dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.04,0:13:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, from what I overheard...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.17,0:13:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,this Hyakkimaru guy got his body parts \Nback from the demons, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.63,0:13:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's causing disasters in this land.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.01,0:13:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.55,0:13:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.56,0:13:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If he gives his body back to the demons...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.39,0:13:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Say that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.44,0:13:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So now you want to live on eating bro up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.23,0:13:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you realize what he went through \Nto get his body back?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.11,0:13:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You've all gone through \Na lot of tough stuff, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.03,0:13:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're fine with making \Nanother human go through worse?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.20,0:13:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just like the samurai \Nand the demons, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.79,0:14:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, we're not saying \Nit's right or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.79,0:14:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But consider it this way. \NIt's your bro or a whole domain...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.13,0:14:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-You little...! \N-Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.09,0:14:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But they said that the land \Nis more important than bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.81,0:14:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And it must be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.02,0:14:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.81,0:14:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-You don't care about... \N-But.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.65,0:14:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That kind of prosperity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.11,0:14:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Peace built upon the sacrifice of one \Nis but fragile.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.70,0:14:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that painfully well now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.83,0:14:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The years of prosperity in our land.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.95,0:14:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It was thanks to the sacrifice \Nof just one, Hyakkimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.46,0:14:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We were but chicks being fed by the hen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.05,0:14:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We stood here, mouths open, \Njust devouring what was fed to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.55,0:14:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What we do not obtain with our own hands, \Nwe cannot protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.69,0:15:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.40,0:15:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I have not the power  \N to stop my own children.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.44,0:15:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,With our own hands, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.62,0:15:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We've always had things taken from us \Nby samurai and wars.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.20,0:15:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But just complaining about \Nsamurai and wars doesn't change a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.96,0:15:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We still end up waiting for the samurai \Nto do something for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.63,0:15:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If we want to protect something...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.22,0:15:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's something we want...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.93,0:15:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to get it like bro is doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.15,0:15:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to grab it with our own two hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.73,0:15:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to be strong to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.19,0:15:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to become stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.07,0:15:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.12,0:15:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.87,0:16:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw them fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You could turn into a demon \Nas you pursue strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.46,0:16:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Or you could let go of all power \Nand not fight anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.05,0:16:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be the path \Nof Buddha and of mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.47,0:16:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But either way,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.14,0:16:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll no longer be human.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.36,0:16:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord! Another Asakura army \Nhas emerged in the east.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.65,0:16:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There are about 1,500 of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.03,0:16:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring men around from \NMitsutoshi's regiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.49,0:16:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We mustn't let them pass, \Nor they'll reach us in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.45,0:16:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell the men to fend them off \Nat whatever cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.50,0:16:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.80,0:16:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If I do, all that's happened this far \Nwill amount to a mere dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.43,0:16:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.14,0:17:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I mustn't let that happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.69,0:17:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I, the lord, cannot have made \Nthe wrong decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.53,0:17:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.57,0:17:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master is fighting a demon-like boy \Nat the two pines.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They say the fighting was abnormal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.24,0:17:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, abnormal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.12,0:17:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not know, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.79,0:17:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He only has Mutsu and Hyogo with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.96,0:17:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no troops I can send to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.01,0:17:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Worry not, \NTahomaru is the heir of Daigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.84,0:17:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He will be victorious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.93,0:17:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't lose to a demon's leftovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.06,0:17:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall fight, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.86,0:17:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I will go to defend the east.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.57,0:17:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Get ready to march!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.74,0:18:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.87,0:18:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That is how it must be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.83,0:18:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Young Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.92,0:18:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody, vacate the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.05,0:18:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A demon will come any minute now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.26,0:18:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Run if you value your lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.05,0:18:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.47,0:18:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No human either way, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.44,0:18:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans can only struggle \Nbetween the two extremes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.90,0:18:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe that's what makes us human.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.45,0:18:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know till you try.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.28,0:18:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't stop being human \Njust cuz you're strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.70,0:18:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. I've watched bro all this time. \NIt's not about strength. It's about heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.58,0:18:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have a good strong heart, \Nyou won't become a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.88,0:18:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I'm sick of being \Ntossed around by samurai and wars.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.97,0:19:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta protect what's ours \Nby ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.18,0:19:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But how do we obtain that power?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.31,0:19:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We can think about that later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.69,0:19:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We just gotta start now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.52,0:19:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't give up, bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.18,0:19:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Any last words?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.88,0:20:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be hard to fight indoors \Nwith your longer arms now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.01,0:20:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.43,0:20:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Die in this castle where you were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.18,0:20:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Give them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.93,0:20:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,My last missing parts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.15,0:20:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.11,0:20:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the castle burning?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.28,0:20:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Has the enemy come?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.32,0:20:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.20,0:20:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.91,0:20:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.46,0:20:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.66,0:20:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I must go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.42,0:20:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The ones that are fighting up there \Nare my sons.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.67,0:21:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I may not be able to do anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.01,0:21:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,but I am their mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.55,0:21:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.77,0:21:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It is time to do what I must do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.50,0:21:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro, I think I kind of  \N understand something now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.54,0:21:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,About what we need to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.13,0:21:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't do it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.10,0:21:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I need you with me.  \N You have to be there with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.73,0:22:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Let them have your eyes, your arms,  \N your legs, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.77,0:22:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want eyes, I'll be your eyes.  \N I'll be your limbs. So please...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.53,0:22:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't become a demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.62,0:22:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.67,0:22:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.97,0:04:30.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,多宝丸！陸奥に兵庫まで
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:32.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき！\Nおよし！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.02,0:04:36.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんなところへ飛び込んだらひとたまりもない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.94,0:04:37.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,けど止めないと
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.15,0:04:43.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いや…今の百鬼丸にお前さんだってことがわかるかどうか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.36,0:04:46.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あとの3人だって尋常じゃあない。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.45,0:04:51.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,覚えがあるよ、あの気配には。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.91,0:04:55.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,間違いない…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.83,0:04:59.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの地獄堂にあったもんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.09,0:05:01.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,地獄堂…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.59,0:05:02.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんだよそれ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.05,0:05:07.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸の身体を喰らった鬼神の像がある御堂です
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.35,0:05:10.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ただ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.89,0:05:15.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,12あるうちの1つだけ、百鬼丸を喰らい損なって
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.94,0:05:19.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なるほどねぇ。それで合点がいったよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.19,0:05:22.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だから百鬼丸は死なずに生まれ、
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.15,0:05:25.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,鬼神につけ狙われたってわけだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.99,0:05:30.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,喰らい損なった身体を取るためにね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.62,0:05:35.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,じゃあ、この間から鬼神を殺してもあにきの体が戻らないのは…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.12,0:05:37.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戻ってないのはどこだね？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.33,0:05:40.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,両手と…あと目だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.55,0:05:46.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そいつは、あの3人の様子と重なってやしないか？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.97,0:05:53.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あいつらには鬼神の力が宿っている
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.60,0:05:59.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,むごたらしい陣取り合戦さね。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.19,0:06:02.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸とその12体目の鬼神との
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.03,0:06:10.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,すべては…我が夫、醍醐景光が鬼神と交わした約定ゆえ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:15.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この国の繁栄は、百鬼丸の犠牲なくしてあり得ませぬ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.29,0:06:17.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だから多宝丸は…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.67,0:06:19.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.05,0:06:25.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おぉーい！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:27.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そいつを捕まえてくれぇー！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.80,0:06:32.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,\Nあ…待ってよ！\Nおよし！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.31,0:06:41.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,兵庫ー！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:17.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,兵庫！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.33,0:07:38.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,陸奥！兵庫！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.66,0:07:40.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どけっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.69,0:08:09.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もしかしてこの馬…お前の…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.44,0:08:12.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,兵庫！陸奥！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.78,0:08:13.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,若…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.20,0:08:19.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,必ずや…戦…なき…世を…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:23.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,待て！行ってはならぬ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.21,0:08:25.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,陸奥！兵庫！あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:41.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ご冗談でございましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.23,0:08:45.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,若が行くなら、地獄にだってついて行く！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.39,0:09:27.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あ…あにき\N百鬼丸ぅーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.20,0:09:38.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.17,0:09:55.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.72,0:10:00.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.51,0:10:02.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わたくしを…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.35,0:10:07.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,母上、お退がりを
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.69,0:10:08.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,多宝丸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.02,0:10:12.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この期に及んで、またあれに心を寄せられまするか。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.19,0:10:18.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あれは我が国の災い！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.37,0:10:21.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,待て！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.66,0:10:24.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.98,0:10:52.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,畜生とはいえ、親子の情とは厚いもんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.65,0:11:00.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,う…あにき…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:07.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これは俺の手…俺のだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.29,0:11:10.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なのになぜみんな邪魔をする！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.67,0:11:14.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前が取り戻す身体は人の血にまみれたものになる。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.34,0:11:19.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そしてその時、お前は人であり得るのか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.26,0:11:22.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,人…？人とはなんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.68,0:11:23.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,俺は！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.72,0:11:25.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,我が国の災い！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.85,0:11:30.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,違う！俺のものだ！俺が取り戻す！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.10,0:11:32.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それがなぜ悪い！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.58,0:11:48.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,逃がさぬ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.26,0:12:10.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はっ！そうか…腕が戻って間合いが変わったか！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.46,0:12:38.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.96,0:12:44.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前が取り戻す身体は…血に…！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.88,0:12:47.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それでも…俺は！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.16,0:13:08.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうすればあにきを止められるんだよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.41,0:13:14.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さてね…このままじゃあどっちかが死ぬまで止まらないだろうねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.04,0:13:19.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あのよ。さっきから聞いてる話じゃあ、
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.17,0:13:24.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その百鬼丸ってのが鬼神から身体を取り返したってんで、
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.63,0:13:27.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この国はおかしくなっちまったんだよな？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.01,0:13:29.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だからなんだよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.55,0:13:31.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いや…まぁ…つまり、
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.56,0:13:34.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,また身体を鬼神に渡せば
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.39,0:13:35.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんだとこのやろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.44,0:13:40.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前ら…こんどはお前らがあにきを食いモンにする気かよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.23,0:13:44.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきがどんなに苦労して身体取り戻したと思ってんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.11,0:13:48.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前らだって、さんざん酷い目に遭ってきたじゃねぇか！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.03,0:13:52.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なのに他の人間を酷い目に遭わせても平気なのか！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.20,0:13:57.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前らも、武士や鬼神と同じんなるのかよ！バカヤロ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.79,0:14:01.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よせ。俺たちだって、それがいいとは思ってねぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.79,0:14:06.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ただよ。もし、お前のあにき1人と、国1つを比べたら…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.13,0:14:09.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前ー！\Nおよしよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.09,0:14:13.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,けど…こいつらあにきより国のほうが大事だって
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.81,0:14:15.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それはそうなのでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.02,0:14:17.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はっ…あんた…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.81,0:14:21.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんたやっぱりあにきのことなんか！\Nでも。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.65,0:14:24.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そんな方法は…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.11,0:14:28.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何者かに頼って築く平安は脆い。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.70,0:14:31.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それが骨身に滲みてわかりました
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.83,0:14:36.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この十数年続いた我が国の繁栄、それは…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.95,0:14:40.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸ただ1人の犠牲でもたらされたもの
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.46,0:14:45.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わたくしたちは…親に餌をもらう雛鳥のようなもの。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.05,0:14:49.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ただ口を開け、喰らっていただけに過ぎませぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.55,0:14:55.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,自らの手で掴まなかったものは、守ることもまたできない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.69,0:15:01.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わたくしにはもう…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.40,0:15:04.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,我が子を止めることさえできませぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.44,0:15:09.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,自分の手で…か
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.62,0:15:17.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいらたちはいつも、武士や戦にいろんなもん持ってかれちまってた。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.20,0:15:23.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,でも…それで戦や侍に文句言ってたって、ダメなんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.96,0:15:27.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,結局武士になんとかしてもらうしかねぇってことだもんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.63,0:15:30.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,守りたいもんがあるなら…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.22,0:15:33.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,欲しいもんが…あるなら…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.93,0:15:40.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきみたいに、自分の手で…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.15,0:15:45.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,地べた這いつくばったって掴まなきゃいけねぇんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.73,0:15:49.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そのためには強くなんなきゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.19,0:15:52.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,力をつけるんだ。自分が
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.07,0:15:54.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なるほどね。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.12,0:15:56.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だがお気をつけよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.87,0:16:00.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さっきの戦いを見たろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:04.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,力を求めて行きつく先は、修羅鬼神かもしれないよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.46,0:16:08.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,と言って力を持たず、争わず
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.05,0:16:14.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,仏の道\N情けの道を行けば
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.47,0:16:17.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どちらに振り切れても…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.14,0:16:21.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,人じゃなくなっちまうのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.36,0:16:32.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,殿！東の守りに、新たな朝倉の手勢が。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.65,0:16:34.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その数、およそ1500！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.03,0:16:37.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,光俊の軍から兵を回せ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.49,0:16:40.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そこを落とされては、一気に懐に入られる。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.45,0:16:44.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,命を懸けても踏みとどまれと伝えよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.50,0:16:51.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,負けるわけにはいかぬ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.80,0:16:56.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ここで負けては今までのことがすべて虚しい夢、幻となる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.43,0:16:59.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,すべて…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.14,0:17:05.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そんなことがあってはならぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.69,0:17:09.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,領主であるわしが…間違っていたなど！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.53,0:17:11.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,殿！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.57,0:17:17.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,若君様が、\N二本松で鬼神の如き男と戦いに及んでいるとのことですが…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:20.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そのご様子が尋常ではないと
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.24,0:17:23.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,尋常ではないとはどういうことだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.12,0:17:25.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それがよく…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.79,0:17:29.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ともかく、手勢は陸奥どのと兵庫どののみと
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.96,0:17:32.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今そっちへ回せる兵はない。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.01,0:17:36.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,心配無用。多宝丸は醍醐の跡継ぎじゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.84,0:17:39.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,必ず勝利するであろう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.93,0:17:47.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あのような鬼の喰い残しなどに負けるはずがない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.06,0:17:49.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,このわしも…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.86,0:17:55.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,東の守り、わしが出る！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.57,0:17:56.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,支度せい！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.74,0:18:01.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.87,0:18:05.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうでなくてはならぬ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.83,0:18:11.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わ…若！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.92,0:18:13.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,全員城を出よ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.05,0:18:17.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もうすぐここへ鬼神が来る。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.26,0:18:19.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,命が惜しければすぐに逃げよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.05,0:18:21.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,は…はっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.47,0:18:26.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どっちにしても人じゃねぇ…か
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.44,0:18:32.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,人は結局、その狭間でもがいていくしかないのかもしれませぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.90,0:18:37.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,逆に言やぁ、だからこそ人でいられるって事で
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.45,0:18:39.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そんなのやってみなきゃわからねぇよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.28,0:18:43.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,力をつけたからって人でなくなるわけじゃねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.70,0:18:49.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいら、あにきと散々見てきたからわかる。\N力じゃねぇ、心持ちさ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.58,0:18:52.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そいつがしっかりしてりゃ、鬼になんかならねぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.88,0:18:59.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうだ。もう武士にも戦にもオロオロするのはこりごりだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.97,0:19:03.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,自分たちのことは自分たちで守るしかねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.18,0:19:07.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,しかし…その力をどうやって手に入れるかだが…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.31,0:19:10.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そんなのはこれから考えりゃいい。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.69,0:19:12.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,とにかく始めるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.52,0:19:14.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だからあにきも…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.18,0:19:49.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もう…話すことはないな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.88,0:20:18.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,腕が伸びたぶん…屋内では不利だな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.01,0:20:24.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.43,0:20:28.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,生まれたこの城で…死ね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.18,0:20:30.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,返せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.93,0:20:32.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,俺の最後の！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.15,0:20:37.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おい、あれ見ろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.11,0:20:43.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,城が燃えてるんじゃねぇか？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.28,0:20:44.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,敵が攻めてきたのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.32,0:20:47.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いや…おそらくあれは…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.20,0:20:49.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきなんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.91,0:20:51.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おい！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.46,0:20:53.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前さん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.66,0:20:55.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,行かねばなりませぬ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.42,0:20:59.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あそこで戦っているのが、わたくしの息子たちならば
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.67,0:21:02.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何もできずとも。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.01,0:21:06.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ただ、2人の母として！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.55,0:21:09.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.77,0:21:15.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わしの…なすべきことを
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.50,0:21:40.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき…おいら、ちょっとだけに何か見えたかもしれねぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.54,0:21:44.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これからのこと、何をするかってこと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.13,0:21:49.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,でも…おいら1人じゃねぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.10,0:21:52.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきも一緒だ！あにきもいなきゃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.73,0:22:00.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もう目ん玉でも手でも足でも鬼神にくれてやれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.77,0:22:04.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,欲しけりゃおいらが目になってやる！手足んなってやる！だから！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.53,0:22:13.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,鬼んなっちゃダメだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.62,0:22:14.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,死んじゃダメだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.67,0:22:20.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.87,0:22:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Born into this world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.53,0:22:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no salvation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.12,0:22:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The distorted shape of the heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.50,0:23:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet it beats courageously
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.84,0:23:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no turning back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.05,0:23:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Even from the path of evil
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.09,0:23:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Witnessing the withering seasons
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.51,0:23:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We search for the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.60,0:23:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,In our ugliness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.43,0:23:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,we don't even recognize the pain
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.94,0:23:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,As we peel back the skin
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.98,0:23:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We are forever tormented by our stupidity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.66,0:23:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But if the dawn never comes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.16,0:23:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Through the painful night
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.25,0:23:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You who distrusts nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.62,0:23:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be able to love  \N this accursed world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.42,0:23:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that we carry the world  \N on our shoulders
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.84,0:23:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to take it back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.05,0:23:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,"Tahomaru"
